Beautiful Severn Model Home Located In Sought-After Somerset Crossing In The Heart Of Gainesville.

12225 Tall Pines Court - Fairfax VA 
$839,000
4 Bed / 4 Bath 
.47 Private Acre Lot 
Heated Pool 

Welcome to this exquisite home nestled in a highly sought-after community surrounded by beautiful trees and tucked away in a peaceful cul-de-sac. You’’ll love the well-maintained house sitting on a spacious half-acre lot that backs onto the serene Piney Branch Stream Valley Parkland, offering stunning views from every window. Get ready to enjoy the good life with a fantastic pool and deck in the backyard, perfect for relaxing and outdoor fun. And here’’s a bonus: no homeowner’’s association (HOA)! Appreciate the nearby Village Drive Village and nearby schools which are Willow Springs Elementary, Katherine Johnson Middle, and Fairfax High School. Commuting and getting around is a breeze with easy access to Rt 29, Fairfax County Parkway, I-66, Rt 50, and the Vienna Metro just minutes away. You’’ll have the best of both worlds - a peaceful retreat surrounded by nature, yet still close to shopping and dining. Fair Oaks Mall, Fairfax Corner, Fair Lakes Shopping Center, and Fair Lakes Promenade are all nearby, offering endless options for your retail therapy and dining adventures.
